angal,serif\">कटा</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">हुआ</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">चिकन</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">डालकर</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">थोड़ी</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">देर</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">पकाये।</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">कॉर्नफ्लोर</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">का</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">घोल</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">मिलाकर</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">गाढ़ा</span><span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">होने</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">तक</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">पकाये।एक</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">दूसरे</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">पैन</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">में</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">नूडल्स</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">को</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">उबालकर</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">पानी</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">निथार</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">लें।</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">कड़ाही</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">में</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">तेल</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">गरम</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">करके</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">उबले</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">हुए</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">नूडल्स</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">को</span><span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">सुनहरा</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">फ्राइड</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">कर</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">लें।</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">मनचाऊ</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">चिकन</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">हूप</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">को</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">फ्राइड</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">नूडल्स</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">से</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">सजाकर</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">सर्व</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">करें।</span></span></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-left:36pt\">\r\n<h4 style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:15px\"><span style=\"color:#5e5e5e\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Poppins\"><span style=\"font-family:mangal,serif\">CLICK HERE TO READ:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://recipeclick.blogspot.in/2018/01/paneer-spring-roll-recipe-how-to-make.html\" style=\"outline:0px; transition:all 0.3s ease; text-decoration:none; color:#ff7700\" target=\"_blank\">पनीर स्प्रिंग रोल्स रेसिपी । Paneer Spring Roll Recipe । How to make Paneer Spring Roll</a></span></span></span></span></span></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 3, '2018-03-05 11:35:36');

